Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:59.74,small,,0,0,0,,衛宮士郎真是棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.74,small,,0,0,0,,我沒說錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:04.25,small,,0,0,0,,再加上美綴綾子 和 間桐慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.79,small,,0,0,0,,這回能拿下新人戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可是藤村老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:18.89,small,,0,0,0,,哪怕在一年級裡 衛宮他也有點別具一格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也說不上來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大賽之前因為打工而受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,給大家添麻煩是想怎麼著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有慎二和美綴在 就算沒有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.97,anotation,,0,0,0,,{\frz340\pos(960,238.333)}不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.97,anotation,,0,0,0,,{\frz340\pos(912,425)}等養好了身體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.97,anotation,,0,0,0,,{\frz340\pos(882.667,598.333)}再回來進行社團活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.97,anotation,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6D7C7E&\pos(848,1022.333)\frz327.1}一會來看你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,同調 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,基本骨架 解明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,構成材質 解明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,基本骨架 變更
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,構成材質 補強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是慎二的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,間桐櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 我來探望你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,肩膀怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那樣的 總之不是你想的那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,以前我也是一個人挺過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也不能讓朋友的妹妹來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,作為士郎的監護人立場 我也不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,家務全部由我包了不用擔心的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 偶爾遇上就一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是今天的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.37,small,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\bord0.1\fs30\frz352\frx13\fry-17\pos(1008.667,333.666)\c&HC5C5C5&\3c&HE3FDFF&\3a&H54&}深山煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.37,small,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\bord0.1\fs24\frz352\frx13\fry-17\pos(1027.867,359.266)\c&HC5C5C5&\3c&HE3FDFF&\3a&H54&}昨天晚上8點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.37,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\shad4\bord1\blur5\frz346\frx10\fry-13\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\pos(907.333,669.667)}在海上觀賞盛大煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,餐具放在上面的櫃子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,下面是米櫃和菜刀 以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,首先從背面開始 從肩膀中間的地方折過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,袖子與折痕平行疊好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,另一面也一樣 小心不要散了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣也算可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那就從頭開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,明天再見哦 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一年半前的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我輸給了那位比我小但是出乎意料般頑固的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,隨著季節變化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,肩膀的傷好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那樣的生活並沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不知是櫻的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還是我自己的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這些或許都不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,發生變化的那就是我不再參加社團活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想多打些工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,本來就是為了鍛煉身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣也好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,還是我自己的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,自己家的鑰匙不怎麼常用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,呀吼～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎一直在模仿切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要成為正義的伙伴之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,胡扯什麼呢 你個醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣先生是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩的父親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對士郎來說切嗣是英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,以至於想去模仿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,小櫻也有這種對象的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是衛宮嗎 來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是慎二的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你對弓道有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥也在搞肯定有興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,…櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那就加入弓道部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:04.75,up,,0,0,0,,還是說已經決定要加入的社團了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:05.83,up,,0,0,0,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.25,up,,0,0,0,,那就來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是強硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.26,small,,0,0,0,,喂 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,藤姐你也是老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大家來笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,投影 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.66,small,,0,0,0,,Trace On
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,又必須得拆開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:51.97,up,,0,0,0,,小櫻 今天晚上吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.98,up,,0,0,0,,拿到些很不錯的茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:56.44,up,,0,0,0,,所以晚上吃辣汁通心粉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.86,up,,0,0,0,,哇 真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,古老的記憶被火焰的顏色充滿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這也許是在告訴我不得沉浸往事之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都會在夢中到達同一個終點站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這是讓我該醒醒了的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 櫻你不用每天都來我家的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有你自己的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 我的興趣就只有做飯和拉弓了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴你哦 我將來的目標是做飯超越前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且前輩馬上就要進入我的射程範圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是每天都在偷學我家秘笈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 做好準備哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且如果不在前輩家 我會覺得吃不下飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不抓緊時間 就趕不上晨練了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮你在和間桐的妹妹交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不 看見你們樂樂呵呵一起上學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是我好朋友的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哪兒可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,還有既然都看見了就打聲招呼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,貧僧還在修行期間 沒有這種肚量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 修好一台了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 衛宮 一大早又來多管閒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不嫌事多 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,閒著也是閒著嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二要是有什麼事也可以來找我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不擅長拉弦和修弓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,已經和弓道部沒關係了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要瞎管閒事也為你自己好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.67,small,,0,0,0,,首先是發音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:07.17,small,,0,0,0,,就算是同樣的後綴也不一定是同樣的發音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.55,small,,0,0,0,,這裡容易錯要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一起吃午飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天我去食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那人是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是二年級的遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是遠坂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,遠坂凜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你認識她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她很有名啊 還很顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,遠坂前輩既漂亮又帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,已經決定不回弓道部了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去慎二他會不樂意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥一定是不擅長面對前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但他比其他人更欣賞你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是個不直率的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥嘴上說討厭但是心裡其實是相反的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這性格可真讓人為難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,蟲子的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,現在可是冬天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我孫女受你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫衛宮士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是慎二的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,愛因茲貝倫家的女兒她還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,又是這個夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我被切嗣救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再不快點召喚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,會死的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,下一條新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.02,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H755A3F&\fad(0,300)\shad3\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(960,766)\4c&HFFFFFF&}肇事車輛涉嫌逃逸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.39,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H755A3F&\fad(300,0)\shad3\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(960,766)\4c&HFFFFFF&}新都商業街煤氣洩漏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,昨日深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,冬木市新都大型建築中發生大規模煤氣洩漏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩拿下盤子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早飯也沒怎麼吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,晨練可以不用去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,顧問都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有事拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,今天放學能盡量早點回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.02,small,,0,0,0,,插播一條緊急新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,今日凌晨冬木市深山町住宅發現四位居民的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:21:00.15,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H755A3F&\shad3\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(960,766)\4c&HFFFFFF&}深山町發生殺人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:20:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,根據冬木市警察局的公佈的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,死者均是被銳利的刀刃殺害 目前警察…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:19.10,small,,0,0,0,,衛宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.67,small,,0,0,0,,衛宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.30,small,,0,0,0,,衛宮！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 美綴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你聽說昨天深山町發生了殺人事件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,殺人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,犯人抓到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,放學後的社團活動必須停止了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,柳洞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,過來一下好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉衛宮 剩下的事一會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是一年級的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二 今天不是說沒有社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.51,0:22:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就算沒有社團我也有很多事要忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然你也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要讓美綴太為難
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你個外人有什麼資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我也拜託你一點事好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在無聊的弓道部裡進行無聊的掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是你的活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說了嗎 我還有事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是閒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就幫我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.24,0:23:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那就將你那老好人做到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:49.88,up,,0,0,0,,今日放學後的社團活動停止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:55.49,up,,0,0,0,,各位職工和學生請在18點之前離校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.43,0:24:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,去那家店裡瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 我也挺想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.88,0:24:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有點專心過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,回家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.03,0:25:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.94,0:25:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.97,0:25:55.45,small,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.56,0:25:57.36,small,,0,0,0,,必須逃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.40,0:25:59.49,small,,0,0,0,,不逃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.53,0:26:01.20,small,,0,0,0,,會死
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.66,0:26:31.23,small,,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.20,0:28:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.23,0:28:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,何等不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.29,0:28:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,何等失敗的召喚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.84,0:28:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,演員雖然湊齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.19,0:28:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但演員質量和舞台完成度都遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.18,0:28:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的聖杯戰爭與我們期望的大儀式差得太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.32,0:28:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.90,0:28:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,既然已經開始那就不能取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.00,0:28:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,杯子裡的水既然滿了 就必須有人喝掉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.08,0:28:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,萬幸教會派來的的監督是那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.29,0:29:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,能好好掌控這次扭曲的聖杯戰爭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.40,0:29:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,聖杯呼喚英靈 英靈需要契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.52,0:29:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,既然被這個儀式所波及
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.20,0:29:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,無論是什麼人 互相廝殺乃是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.23,0:29:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要最後還剩下一人足矣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.24,0:29:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,第七位受到召喚的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.33,0:29:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是那個Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.83,0:29:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是衛宮的子嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.55,0:29:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是奇妙的因緣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.88,0:29:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,教會是不可侵犯地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.22,0:29:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不能出手
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.14,0:29:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.45,0:29:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那個男人究竟是不是適合詠頌福音的聖者
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.37,0:30:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.32,0:30:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道為什麼你這樣的廢柴魔術師能被選為Master
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.01,0:30:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來我們要見的這個人 要好好聽他介紹聖杯戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.58,0:30:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是個讓人討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.59,0:30:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對這三番四次的呼叫本想不作理睬
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.86,0:30:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但卻帶來了個奇怪的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.54,0:30:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他即是第七人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.71,0:31:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是言峰綺禮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.05,0:31:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是負責這個教會之人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.84,0:31:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮士郎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.51,0:31:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你是Saber的Master沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.20,0:31:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 我被Saber所救
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.93,0:31:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但Master如果必須是正規魔術師的話 我建議還是重選
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.36,0:31:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,重選Master嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.45,0:31:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.79,0:31:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說 你對10年前發生的事毫不關心咯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.61,0:31:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂聖杯 乃是魔術世界裡的萬能之力
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.13,0:31:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是能實現所有願望的許願機
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.60,0:31:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,為了得到此物 被選上的各位Master互相爭奪 自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.43,0:32:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,結果 最終發生了不幸的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.52,0:32:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是能稱得上是災害的大規模事故
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.98,0:32:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.58,0:32:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.45,0:32:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只要住在這鎮上的人 無人不知
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.44,0:32:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,死傷500人 燒燬的建築多達134棟
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.54,0:32:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,原因直接仍未明瞭的那次火災
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.25,0:32:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,正式聖杯戰爭所留下的烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.43,0:32:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.97,0:32:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,綺禮 我讓你說明規則
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.41,0:32:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒讓你往傷口上撒鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.54,0:32:49.11,small,,0,0,0,,那個聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.75,0:32:50.90,small,,0,0,0,,真的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.82,0:32:52.65,small,,0,0,0,,上回
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.03,0:32:56.45,small,,0,0,0,,有個人暫時得到了聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.53,0:32:59.20,small,,0,0,0,,那個人後來怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.12,0:33:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,並沒有怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.24,0:33:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那個聖杯還未能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.04,0:33:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,迴避戰鬥的人無法得到聖杯的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.38,0:33:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,說得就像是看見過似的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.76,0:33:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.40,0:33:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我作為上回的Master 參與了聖杯的爭奪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.82,0:33:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 這是真的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.47,0:33:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一直戰鬥到中途
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.07,0:33:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但由於判斷錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.32,0:33:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,結果我只得到了聖杯的空殼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.62,0:33:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.69,0:33:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,話題才聊到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.79,0:33:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,來了一位性急的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.72,0:33:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道愛因茲貝倫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.43,0:34:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.27,0:34:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,時間可不多
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.36,0:34:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我聽聽你的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.36,0:34:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.28,0:34:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果說10年前那場災害的原因是聖杯戰爭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.28,0:34:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.21,0:34:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.17,0:34:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,作為Master戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.76,0:34:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,高興吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.30,0:34:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你的願望 終會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.14,0:34:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,正義的伙伴 需要一個被打倒的邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.20,0:34:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant怎麼可能記得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.49,0:35:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,話都聊完了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.21,0:35:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.71,0:35:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.46,0:35:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅蘇菲爾·馮·愛因茲貝倫
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.96,0:35:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.98,0:35:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 殺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.62,0:35:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.11,0:35:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.96,0:36:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.06,0:36:08.68,small,,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.07,0:36:17.04,small,,0,0,0,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.89,0:36:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏Archer不在
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.90,0:36:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.21,0:36:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人會再生
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.33,0:36:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,把她脖子剁下來凌辱她
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.73,0:36:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.91,0:36:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.73,0:36:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.78,0:37:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.69,0:37:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.23,0:37:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.94,0:37:43.49,small,,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.94,0:37:46.41,small,,0,0,0,,真是的 搞什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.46,0:37:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.80,0:38:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很憧憬正義的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,當英雄是有時間限制的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.88,0:38:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦長大成人就不再好這樣自稱了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.10,0:38:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.44,0:38:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,並且
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.06,0:38:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,幫助一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.73,0:38:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,也就意味著不能去幫助另一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.24,0:38:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.24,0:38:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如何才能成為正義的伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.50,0:38:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.93,0:38:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,傷都好了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.47,0:38:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.93,0:38:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.12,0:38:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.10,0:39:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.36,0:39:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這是遠坂你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.57,0:39:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.69,0:39:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這傷口是Master憑您自己的力量痊癒的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.61,0:39:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.88,0:39:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪有這能力
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.70,0:39:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那或許是與Saber之間的契約帶來的影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.29,0:39:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,首先…你給我解釋下剛才到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.03,0:39:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒做錯什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.84,0:39:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,本來應該能更完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.59,0:39:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我們Servant是依靠Master的魔力供給而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.57,0:39:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要是沒有了供給
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.04,0:39:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們無法在這個世界繼續逗留
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.51,0:39:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.01,0:39:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.11,0:39:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就此告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.53,0:39:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也該為自己的Servant做些治療了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.51,0:39:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再見面就是敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.71,0:40:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她真是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.35,0:40:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber你的傷還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.72,0:40:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.76,0:40:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然稱不上完全恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.40,0:40:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.90,0:40:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber你也想得到聖杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.18,0:40:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.11,0:40:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,為此我才會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.62,0:40:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker的Master說她是愛因茲貝倫
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.65,0:40:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的小孩子也會參加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.61,0:40:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.01,0:40:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼人在使用魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.94,0:40:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是Berserker的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.64,0:41:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是完全不同的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.81,0:41:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Master 請下達指示
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.72,0:41:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.98,0:41:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.50,0:41:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有結界
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.90,0:41:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.71,0:41:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.57,0:41:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,美綴
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.67,0:42:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,美綴
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.72,0:42:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是嚇著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.76,0:42:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為誰來了 這不是衛宮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.48,0:42:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.47,0:42:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.06,0:42:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們的弓道部部長稍稍幫了點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.15,0:42:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.40,0:42:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的Servant？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.12,0:42:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,向你介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.12,0:42:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.08,0:42:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 我們打一場試試啊 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.17,0:42:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看Servant之間的戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.49,0:43:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.89,0:43:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要當Master
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.78,0:43:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,間桐可是有名頭的古老魔術師家系
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.53,0:43:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在聖杯戰爭裡 還被人稱作是御三家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.00,0:43:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,本來是不想告訴你這樣的菜鳥的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.11,0:43:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而我作為長子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.70,0:43:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,參加聖杯戰爭 不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.91,0:43:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.16,0:43:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你這人還是這麼不識趣
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.02,0:43:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,都已經明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.44,0:43:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這場遊戲是動真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.34,0:43:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.39,0:44:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.41,0:44:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.99,0:44:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,誰允許你輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.79,0:44:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.75,0:44:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.59,0:45:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.10,0:45:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你這弄得像是我很弱一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.20,0:45:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.85,0:45:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.88,0:45:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快滅掉 滅掉啊 滅…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.36,0:45:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.42,0:45:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,給你的負擔還是太重了呀 慎二
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.55,0:45:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子 間桐就算敗退了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.93,0:45:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,遺憾至極
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.60,0:45:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.84,0:45:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.43,0:45:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是間桐家的魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.94,0:45:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,由我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.50,0:46:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,無能之人做任何事都是無能
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.78,0:46:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,間桐的血脈也算完了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.37,0:46:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,對你不抱任何期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.40,0:46:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.21,0:46:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 請你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.87,0:46:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會連櫻也
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.25,0:46:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也會被逼著做這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.84,0:46:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼會扯到她的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.10,0:46:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,明明有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.47,0:46:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那種廢物她懂魔術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.43,0:46:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,間桐的家訓是屬於我一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.33,0:46:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,美綴
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.17,0:47:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,由於是聖杯戰爭的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.84,0:47:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,交給監督處理會比較妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.06,0:47:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.59,0:47:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,才過幾個小時你就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.41,0:47:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.03,0:47:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,被不祥之物纏身
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.08,0:47:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她暫且由我這裡照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.63,0:48:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.40,0:48:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,美綴怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.30,0:48:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都處理完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.57,0:48:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不用操心
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.20,0:48:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,和她比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.91,0:48:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎你反而更嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.46,0:48:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都好了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.12,0:48:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,10年前的戰鬥之中
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.58,0:48:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經有個人像你一樣受了致命傷還能像沒事人一樣站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.59,0:48:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,此人最後與我展開戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.93,0:48:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,並且成為了上回聖杯戰爭的勝利者
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.23,0:48:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,名為
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.10,0:48:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.49,0:48:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.70,0:48:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,美綴得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.78,0:48:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.24,0:49:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,花了很多時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.79,0:49:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,向他
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.12,0:49:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,問了些切嗣…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.13,0:49:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.22,0:49:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.18,0:49:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有些事我必須告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.02,0:49:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮切嗣這個人 將其概括就是個殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.94,0:49:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,以專殺魔術師為生的魔術師殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.61,0:49:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管魔術師儘是些偏離道德常理之人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.41,0:49:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在這些人之中 他仍顯得與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.47,0:49:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,上回
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.71,0:49:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我被召喚至這個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.21,0:49:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,作為愛因茲貝倫的Servant進行戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.80,0:49:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,當時我的Master名叫
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.87,0:49:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.30,0:49:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.47,0:49:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他簡直是個沒有血肉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.30,0:50:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,為了獲勝 用盡各種手段
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.31,0:50:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕對方Master跪地求饒也毫不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.12,0:50:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在所有人之中
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.36,0:50:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣認定那位神父是他最大的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.44,0:50:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他與我…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.07,0:50:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只有互相廝殺以外沒有其他選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.20,0:50:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.79,0:50:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,共同挑戰聖杯戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.74,0:50:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,獲得勝利直到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.09,0:50:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.58,0:50:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮切嗣背叛了聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.36,0:50:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在那最後的最後
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.76,0:50:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,將
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.53,0:50:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.68,0:50:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.35,0:50:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,為放10人一條生路 殺死1個人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.68,0:50:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一個無可救藥的聖人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.38,0:51:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.51,0:51:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我所認識的切嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.65,0:51:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是不會置聖杯戰爭中犧牲的人們於不顧的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.77,0:51:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我憧憬這樣的正義的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.23,0:51:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也因此投身戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.65,0:51:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這話說得有點晚
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.91,0:51:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.21,0:51:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能與我一同戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.91,0:51:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,無論我過去如何
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.54,0:51:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,刻印的令咒維繫著如今的Master與我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.75,0:51:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能叫我士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.68,0:52:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那就…士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.68,0:52:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我更喜歡這個發音
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.22,0:52:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.19,0:52:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.44,0:52:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.45,0:52:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 你是切嗣的熟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.58,0:52:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是真遭罪 行李居然還沒寄到
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.96,0:52:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,穿著士郎的舊衣服 真對不住 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.25,0:52:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.20,0:52:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,您不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.67,0:52:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣也真是個罪孽深重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.71,0:52:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然知道他經常去國外
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.58,0:52:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,吶吶 好想聽聽你和切嗣的回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.68,0:52:49.43,up,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.10,0:52:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.64,0:52:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,事出突然
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.20,0:52:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.74,0:52:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.11,0:52:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.62,0:52:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,今早遇到慎二了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.29,0:53:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.49,0:53:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.62,0:53:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.42,0:53:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.62,0:53:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.33,0:53:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.73,0:53:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.85,0:53:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.32,0:53:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.22,0:53:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant都不帶就敢來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.24,0:53:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,膽子真是有夠大的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.48,0:53:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是繼續這樣不把我放眼裡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.96,0:54:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我這輩子就求你這一次 遠坂
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.47,0:54:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,聽聽我的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.18,0:54:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.54,0:54:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二是Master 綾子被捲入其中 以及Rider消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.40,0:54:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你要說的不會只是這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.31,0:54:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二有個妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.16,0:54:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,叫櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.34,0:54:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.75,0:54:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻可能也被捲進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.80,0:54:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二那傢伙似乎還沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.81,0:54:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子下去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.58,0:54:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.93,0:54:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,讓她住在你那裡保護她不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.84,0:55:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.59,0:55:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對你來說是很重要的人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.50,0:55:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.26,0:55:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的早餐真的太美味了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.93,0:55:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至還準備了午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.68,0:55:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,允許我再次感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.35,0:55:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡 不用這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.85,0:55:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼可以幫忙的請務必讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.86,0:55:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.82,0:55:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,加油哇
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.08,0:56:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,…那麼就
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.08,0:56:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.88,0:56:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,想著很多東西要用就都買了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.51,0:56:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 Saber 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.59,0:56:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…行李寄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.16,0:56:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呀 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.91,0:56:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.05,0:56:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,老是在麻煩遠坂
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.40,0:56:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.15,0:56:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,需要日用品我能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.57,0:56:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不是太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.62,0:56:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊對了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.16,0:56:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,藤姐
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.43,0:56:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天開始想讓櫻暫時住在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.12,0:56:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 你這心血來潮到底是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.75,0:56:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,最近外面很危險不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.95,0:56:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二那傢伙也似乎很忙不怎麼顧家
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.93,0:56:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.81,0:56:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.29,0:57:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.56,0:57:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我去準備一下Saber小姐的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.08,0:57:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.37,0:57:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.74,0:57:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,原因是不是為了使櫻不要誤解你讓Saber留宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.38,0:57:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.30,0:57:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,小櫻她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.63,0:57:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說是E罩杯
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.40,0:57:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在聊些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.56,0:57:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 櫻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.93,0:57:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.51,0:57:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.52,0:58:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼快我就派上用處了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.84,0:58:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我再多待一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.76,0:58:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我再多陪你半小時 老老實實休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.75,0:58:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.06,0:58:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那就麻煩你照看了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.86,0:58:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.86,0:58:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.74,0:58:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.87,0:58:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,說我可以住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.49,0:58:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.08,0:58:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.79,0:58:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.07,0:58:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.75,0:58:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.92,0:58:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你能住這裡就會好很多
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.17,0:59:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.85,0:59:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.42,0:59:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒料到
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.08,0:59:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,居然是此等蛇蠍摩羯之物
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.52,1:00:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,宗一郎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.78,1:00:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.37,1:00:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你和大家留在這
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.96,1:00:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.17,1:00:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快出來
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.14,1:00:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.61,1:00:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,宗一郎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.03,1:00:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.62,1:00:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這個男人是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.92,1:01:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,先斬了他的項上人頭
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.80,1:01:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,隨後切斷他胳膊 腿
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.08,1:01:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,接著開膛破肚
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.08,1:01:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.45,1:01:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還在動彈
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.15,1:01:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是原本的Assassin嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.69,1:01:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,把我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.32,1:01:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,放開
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.07,1:01:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.35,1:01:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣你滿意了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.84,1:02:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.33,1:03:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.59,1:03:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,隨你…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.03,1:03:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.74,1:03:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,欲
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.77,1:03:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,遠…坂
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.69,1:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.56,1:03:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.72,1:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.01,1:03:53.85,anotation2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H755A3F&\shad3\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(960,760)\4c&HFFFFFF&}新都商業街再發煤氣洩漏
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.26,1:03:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,繼前幾天的原因不明煤氣洩露事故
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.09,1:03:57.64,small,,0,0,0,,冬木市新都的大樓裡又再次發生了煤氣洩露
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.23,1:04:02.15,small,,0,0,0,,昨夜發生煤氣洩露的是新都站以東的商業樓
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.64,1:04:07.11,small,,0,0,0,,樓裡的警衛員和數位員工陷入昏迷
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.99,1:04:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.73,1:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.73,1:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是藤姐啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.24,1:04:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不能來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.11,1:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚我去了柳洞寺
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.96,1:04:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,新都的昏迷事件
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.03,1:04:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡的魔力都流向了柳洞寺
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.76,1:05:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer也已經恢復
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.50,1:05:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,便前去調查了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.97,1:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,得出結論
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.79,1:05:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,據守在柳洞寺的是Caster
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.10,1:05:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.47,1:05:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我抵達時 Caster已經被消滅得乾乾淨淨了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.12,1:05:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,寺裡的居民因魔力被奪而陷入昏迷
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.06,1:05:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而唯一被殺的葛木老師
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.15,1:05:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是Caster的Master
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.09,1:05:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來才是問題
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.28,1:05:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,今早在新都又發生了昏迷事件
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.92,1:05:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Caster都消失了 卻依然
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.09,1:05:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻到底還是在你家住下了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.08,1:06:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天開始留宿在我家
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.78,1:06:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.02,1:06:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不想和我聯手嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.11,1:06:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看來這次和我從父親那聽到的不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.61,1:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想先弄明白究竟發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.87,1:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,限定時間的合作嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.05,1:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.14,1:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,凜
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.30,1:06:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為和沒有實力的Master合作毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.23,1:06:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.64,1:06:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你提了個錯誤的建議
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.19,1:06:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.19,1:06:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你要遵從Master的方針
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.20,1:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,事不宜遲
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.91,1:06:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚出動吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.04,1:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要和Archer的Master聯手嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.83,1:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我擅自作主了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.00,1:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.40,1:07:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,而且早早結束聖杯戰爭 也能讓櫻回歸原本的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.01,1:07:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.04,1:07:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻她是不是身體不太好
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.25,1:07:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.06,1:07:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.31,1:07:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但願只是我的多慮
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.95,1:07:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.10,1:07:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰來了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.67,1:07:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.67,1:07:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是櫻她哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.05,1:08:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把可愛的妹妹帶回家 有什麼不可以的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.80,1:08:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有哥哥會打妹妹的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.88,1:08:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你連累了美綴 我是不會把櫻交給你的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.58,1:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.16,1:08:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這兩天才剛上手
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.78,1:08:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒艹夠還不想放手是不是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.95,1:08:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.61,1:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.01,1:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.55,1:08:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這表情很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.72,1:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,來幹架啊 前幾天的舊賬我們繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.41,1:08:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 住手
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.00,1:08:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.02,1:08:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼我都聽
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.73,1:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,至少在前輩面前請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.18,1:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.63,1:09:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才這話
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.48,1:09:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.67,1:09:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.92,1:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.40,1:09:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這不需要你道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.25,1:10:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 根本無法集中
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.76,1:10:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.18,1:10:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.39,1:10:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是櫻嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.07,1:10:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.20,1:10:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,能陪我
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.96,1:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,聊一會兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.72,1:10:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.30,1:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才哥哥真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.01,1:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不要介意了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.35,1:11:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,冷了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.95,1:11:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,等我一會兒
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.00,1:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.38,1:11:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.38,1:11:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這個修好了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.71,1:11:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,費了很大功夫
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.10,1:11:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.60,1:11:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.46,1:11:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.11,1:11:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.65,1:11:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,還不認識前輩時候的事
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.70,1:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,通紅的晚霞映襯下
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.95,1:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,操場和走廊空無一人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.70,1:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,美麗 卻又帶幾分寂寞
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.19,1:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個人在操場上練習助跑跳高
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.17,1:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我那時並不是個乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.75,1:12:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看著他
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.85,1:12:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,心裡希望那個人快快失敗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.07,1:12:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.41,1:12:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不管跳幾次他都跳不過去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.63,1:12:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,最後他承認自己是跳不過去的 收拾好以後就回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.05,1:12:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.90,1:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這也就是說
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.63,1:12:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.77,1:13:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是現在在我身邊的這位高年級學生
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.48,1:13:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,從那時起我就認識前輩了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.02,1:13:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.57,1:13:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這倒是我第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.87,1:13:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.91,1:13:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.00,1:13:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有件難以啟齒的事能問你嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.75,1:13:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,從藤村老師那裡聽說
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.98,1:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩是被這個家收養的養子
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.55,1:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.39,1:13:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩對此有什麼想法嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.14,1:13:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,花了很長時間才適應
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.90,1:13:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但沒什麼特別在意的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.69,1:13:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是因為你身邊的人都很善良的緣故
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.03,1:14:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我身邊的長輩們都很不靠譜
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.29,1:14:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣做家務完全不行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.79,1:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,藤姐她又是那副德行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.21,1:14:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,做著家務
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.04,1:14:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,然後漸漸就變成了現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.63,1:14:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我想像成為切嗣那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.97,1:14:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,正義的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.23,1:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.40,1:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.53,1:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.45,1:14:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.41,1:14:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有件事想問你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.46,1:14:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.09,1:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我變成了壞人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.67,1:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你會原諒我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.22,1:15:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻如果做了壞事我會生氣
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.01,1:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,比別人更加嚴厲批評你
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.66,1:15:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.27,1:15:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,被前輩批評
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.44,1:15:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我願意
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.99,1:15:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我去睡了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.23,1:15:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.98,1:15:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.47,1:15:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,深山總部呼叫深山各救護車
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.93,1:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,深山總部呼叫深山各救護車
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.52,1:15:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,中心來電
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.06,1:15:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,新都站附近有多名傷者
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.19,1:15:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,請能夠趕來車輛緊急前往救援
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.85,1:16:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你搗的鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.43,1:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.62,1:16:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對個小小沙蟲來說 那還真是難為你了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.03,1:17:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.63,1:19:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,回來
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.24,1:20:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,收手吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.20,1:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,飛行道具是傷不到我的 是我的天賦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.47,1:20:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,流矢的加護嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.80,1:20:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,將塗黑的武器隱匿於黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.84,1:20:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,無聊透頂
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.58,1:21:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到我的臉了吧 Lancer
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.54,1:21:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,現在才開始呢
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.72,1:21:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你對這裡這麼執著
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.60,1:21:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沙蟲跑進水裡還能怎麼著
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.23,1:22:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是不動 可是會被吞沒哦
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.72,1:22:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.32,1:22:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白這是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.49,1:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.79,1:22:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,寶具——
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.64,1:22:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,妄想心音
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.64,1:22:41.89,small,,0,0,0,,Zabaniya
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.43,1:22:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,寶具？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.68,1:22:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管有那麼點遠 在這結果你
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.08,1:23:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,穿刺——
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.08,1:23:03.75,small,,0,0,0,,Gae
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.40,1:23:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,死棘之槍
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.40,1:23:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Blog
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.73,1:23:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.32,1:23:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,輸
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.35,1:23:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.16,1:24:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這展開
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.70,1:24:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.54,1:25:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.45,1:25:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.96,1:25:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,邊走邊說吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.41,1:25:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我們被人盯著呢 做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.51,1:25:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你幹的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.44,1:25:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,間桐家的老爺子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.43,1:25:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是遠坂家的小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.26,1:25:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,優秀 很優秀
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.46,1:25:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,臟硯
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.50,1:25:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,間桐家不是敗退了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.61,1:26:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人可沒說過半句認輸的話
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.37,1:26:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.90,1:26:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.03,1:26:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然褻瀆英靈的屍體
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.84,1:26:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,何等惡毒
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.34,1:26:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber 不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.80,1:26:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,碰那把劍
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.89,1:26:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要碰這把劍
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.99,1:27:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這把劍是破魔劍
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.53,1:27:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕能斬斷和Master之間的契約
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.08,1:27:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.21,1:27:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,本打算迅速解決的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.07,1:27:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,確實她的魔術對Saber不起作用
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.45,1:27:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不過連帶上Master又會如何呢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.84,1:28:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.38,1:28:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.73,1:28:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.08,1:28:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.51,1:28:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.76,1:28:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看那邊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.32,1:28:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.84,1:28:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.58,1:28:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,虛數空間
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.88,1:28:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.02,1:28:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.51,1:28:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.89,1:29:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Caster
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.54,1:29:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.65,1:29:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.80,1:29:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.35,1:29:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.10,1:29:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有被本體直接觸碰到
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.40,1:29:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是沾上些灰塵的程度
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.32,1:29:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.73,1:29:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道剛才那是什麼怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.68,1:29:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那誰知道
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.20,1:29:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不過最近
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.61,1:30:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在吸收城裡人們魔力的應該就是那道影子
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.73,1:30:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.75,1:30:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.55,1:30:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看來 已經容不得我再糾結私人恩怨了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.43,1:30:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.53,1:30:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.87,1:30:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明明有我陪著可還是…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.55,1:30:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我來
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.29,1:30:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,否則學長只會繼續痛苦下去
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.02,1:31:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.74,1:31:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 特意喊你出來
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.30,1:31:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我來得早所以先吃起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.51,1:31:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.88,1:31:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.51,1:31:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,誰要吃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.72,1:31:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,到底要跟我說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.13,1:31:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.36,1:31:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚你看到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.16,1:32:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.51,1:32:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是以我的方式在觀察這次的聖杯戰爭
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.01,1:32:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,關於柳洞寺 我已經收到了凜提交的報告
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.41,1:32:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我和間桐臟硯交手了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.46,1:32:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然他帶著Caster
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.22,1:32:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但那
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.92,1:32:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎是在操縱屍體
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.97,1:32:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那個老爺子也終於出手了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.28,1:32:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.65,1:32:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來我告訴你一件凜都不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.36,1:32:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Caster在柳洞寺被殺當晚
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.32,1:32:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個Servant衝破結界逃了出去
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.32,1:32:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.33,1:32:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.20,1:32:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.62,1:32:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.88,1:33:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我的Lancer看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.71,1:33:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴過你 我曾經也是一名Master
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.69,1:33:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.05,1:33:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.10,1:33:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.52,1:33:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我命令Lancer去監視Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.53,1:33:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,追到柳洞寺就沒有再回來
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.56,1:33:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是被Assassin幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.83,1:33:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassin往往會依賴自己擅長的氣息遮斷能力
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.63,1:33:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而自身的戰鬥力並不強
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.30,1:33:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,正常交手Lancer應該不會輸
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.93,1:33:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,衛宮士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.76,1:33:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你昨天看到的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.64,1:33:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大概不止間桐臟硯和Caster吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.58,1:34:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕Assassin是知道這一點才把Lancer引過去的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.37,1:34:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,藏在那裡的東西不僅僅只對Servant下手
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.96,1:34:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,連街上的市民也不放過
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.63,1:34:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果將Caster吸取人類魔力的行為比作抽血的話
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.18,1:34:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而那東西就相當於
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.43,1:34:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,進食
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.28,1:34:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,若是這樣置其於不顧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.65,1:34:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這座城鎮會變成無人之都
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.52,1:34:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,失去意識的竟然多達30人
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.42,1:35:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,地點在深山南四丁目
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.05,1:35:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡有什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.18,1:35:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,柳洞寺
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.06,1:35:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.35,1:35:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你不吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.27,1:35:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是死也不會和你一起吃飯
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.76,1:35:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.60,1:35:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.11,1:36:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,話說
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.12,1:36:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻她還住在你家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.59,1:36:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.57,1:36:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.53,1:36:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣起碼不會被一無所知的她突然撞見了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.75,1:36:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我準備去追蹤臟硯
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.36,1:36:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,去間桐家
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.88,1:36:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.84,1:36:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我和間桐家有孽緣
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.27,1:36:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老一代魔術師之間的鬥爭就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.32,1:36:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 衛宮
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.60,1:36:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.51,1:36:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.45,1:36:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道前輩和你到底在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.76,1:36:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我問相信你們也不會告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.33,1:36:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.55,1:37:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩他昨晚是受了傷回到家的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.17,1:37:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.71,1:37:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩他受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.72,1:37:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.30,1:37:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,去追蹤那個黑影
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.01,1:37:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不能放著不管
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.34,1:37:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,已經有無辜的人被捲進來了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.32,1:37:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.41,1:37:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們就繼續維持休戰協議
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.32,1:37:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,遠坂
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.12,1:37:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不會放過那個黑影
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.11,1:37:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.19,1:37:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.12,1:37:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,直到搞清楚那個東西是什麼為止
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.79,1:37:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.69,1:38:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我被櫻埋怨了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.19,1:38:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,昨夜
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.75,1:38:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒能保護好士郎是因為我能力不足
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.41,1:38:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那只能怪我自己倒下了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.12,1:38:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要說問題在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.80,1:38:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,還是因為我沒能阻止士郎你去投身戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.43,1:38:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.38,1:38:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我會與你並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.13,1:38:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,保護你
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.14,1:38:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.47,1:38:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,同時也是
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.76,1:38:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,為了櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.24,1:39:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼玩意
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.33,1:39:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.50,1:39:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.76,1:39:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 是Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.57,1:39:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你就呆在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.40,1:39:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.33,1:39:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂飛蛾撲火 說的就是你這種吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.44,1:39:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,間桐
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.24,1:39:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,臟硯
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.88,1:39:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那陣風
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.10,1:39:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然被正面擊中的話會很危險
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.32,1:39:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,風啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.60,1:40:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,肆虐吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.49,1:40:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,避風的加護
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.73,1:40:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對時常行走於沙漠之人而言是必備的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.45,1:40:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你不攻過來也無妨
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.00,1:40:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但可別忘了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.54,1:40:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的御主正在盛情款待你家御主呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.05,1:40:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.71,1:40:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要吸引你的注意就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.22,1:41:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassin 你…
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.41,1:41:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant是無法反抗這個黑影的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.52,1:41:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕純粹如你 只要被它碰一下也會失去理智
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.21,1:41:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但在那之前
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.46,1:41:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心臟
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.09,1:41:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就由我收下了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.14,1:41:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,投影 開始
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.14,1:41:27.72,small,,0,0,0,,Trace On
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.69,1:41:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就憑一根木棍能幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.49,1:41:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,妄想心音
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.49,1:41:51.91,small,,0,0,0,,Zabaniya
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.97,1:42:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.73,1:42:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是最強的Servant
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.42,1:42:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,與其被奪走心臟
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.84,1:42:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,卻選擇了同自身的黑暗做鬥爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.20,1:43:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,看來已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.99,1:43:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你身為Master應該知道
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.33,1:43:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你的Servant已經從這個世上消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.50,1:43:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你個混賬
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.17,1:44:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,之後就交給你了 Assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.16,1:46:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.94,1:46:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.35,1:46:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.75,1:46:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber——
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.82,1:47:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.92,1:47:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是個
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.13,1:47:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.42,1:47:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.49,1:47:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說 我
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.96,1:48:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不再
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.32,1:48:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是一名Master了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.06,1:48:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.85,1:48:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,居然是修煉場
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.23,1:48:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,居然
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.44,1:48:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,居然會有這種東西
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.82,1:49:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該會看不起我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.24,1:49:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,用他人的生命來延續自己腐朽的身體
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.41,1:49:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.29,1:49:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,您對生命的執著
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.09,1:49:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,正是作為吾主所應具備的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.36,1:49:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡有鷹
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.45,1:49:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,您是說鷹嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.49,1:49:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,塞拉
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.58,1:49:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,給我準備一輛車
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.44,1:50:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明天開始我也要去城裡
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.21,1:50:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道是哪位
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.97,1:50:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但這是屬於愛因茲貝倫的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.56,1:50:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.85,1:50:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.20,1:50:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.61,1:50:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.57,1:50:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.44,1:50:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是聖杯
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.83,1:50:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.50,1:50:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為了得到它
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.62,1:50:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我都說了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.04,1:50:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.42,1:51:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.55,1:51:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不允許你阻止我
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.40,1:51:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你問我
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.94,1:51:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.72,1:51:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這種問題
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.94,1:51:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不是一目了然嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.77,1:52:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,前…
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.44,1:52:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,輩…
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.34,1:52:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.34,1:52:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,又受了這樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.42,1:52:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,請多珍惜一下自己的身體
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.48,1:52:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.00,1:52:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.74,1:52:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.68,1:52:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.91,1:52:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.07,1:52:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.44,1:53:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.42,1:53:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.01,1:53:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.97,1:53:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我實在不明白
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.36,1:53:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.11,1:53:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎麼做
